data.title: Amritsar: Urban/Semi Urban Colonies and Their Patwar Details Situated Within Sub Division Amritsar - 1
data.meta_description: sdmasr1Amritsar.pdf - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. This document lists details of urban and semi-urban colonies located within Sub Division Amritsar-1, including their revenue estate, names and addresses of patwaris and kanungos responsible for each colony. It contains 32 entries listing colony names, corresponding revenue estates, and contact information for the responsible revenue officials.
